summary: ‪2/17コミティア/有難うございました！ 「Good Morning」p24 朝の愛しさにまつわる本をつくりました。暮らしや ひなたや 洗濯物とかです。  朝に恋人たちが、いちゃいちゃしてるだけっていう 煩悩だらけのかんじなのですが...
caption:
‪2/17コミティア/有難うございました！

「Good Morning」p24 朝の愛しさにまつわる本をつくりました。暮らしや ひなたや 洗濯物とかです。 

朝に恋人たちが、いちゃいちゃしてるだけっていう 煩悩だらけのかんじなのですが ノンバイナリーテーマを ゆるくやさしく感じて たのしんでもらえたら 嬉しいです
どうぞよろしくお願いします。* 是非遊びにきてください。‬

「Good Morning」
A5 p24 ‘COMITIA’ 2/17
✴︎ 「Good Morning」 artbook  illustration and graphic

I made a book on morning love. It is living, sunflower and laundry.

It is the contents lovers love in the morning. It shows exactly my feelings. However, through this book, I am happy if you enjoy the theme of non binary, love it and enjoy it.

summary:
So uh
I finished the (Spoiler) art
And I liked how it turned out
Now I wanted to put this as my AU (where the prince actually...
body:
So uh

I finished the (Spoiler) art

And I liked how it turned out

Now I wanted to put this as my AU (where the prince actually saw the wolf and didn’t get blinded) to post this without spoiling the game but no one knows that AU and there’s no point in that AU so I decided to not tag it as my AU

And I’m pretty scared

Because I have a friend on here who didn’t want to get spoiled over the game’s storyline

So I have that to worry

And I can’t ask them if they finished the game

Because I’m shy/can’t talk to them normally and they haven’t answered my last message (Probably because they’re busy)

So if you see this I’m really sorry for spoiling the game for you

(Again, not tagging them because NOT RISKING IT)

But I have completed this game

And I want more of this

Like DLC or something
